{{> layout/header}}
    <div class="fh-wrapper">
        <header class="fh-navbar bg-white bg-opacity-80 backdrop-blur-md sticky-top">
            <div class="navbar-brand">
                <div class="brand-icon shadow-sm"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">forest</span></div>
                <h1 class="brand-name">Forest Haven</h1>
            </div>
            <nav class="d-none d-lg-flex gap-5">
                <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none text-dark fw-bold small hover-primary">리뷰</a>
                <a href="/galleries" class="text-decoration-none text-dark fw-bold small hover-primary">포토갤러리</a>
                <a href="/qna" class="text-decoration-none text-primary fw-bold small border-bottom border-primary border-2 pb-1">QnA</a>
                <a href="21실시간예약.html" class="text-decoration-none text-dark fw-bold small hover-primary">예약하기</a>
            </nav>
            <button onclick="location.href='01마이페이지홈.html'" class="btn btn-primary px-4 py-2 small fw-bold shadow-sm rounded-pill">마이페이지</button>
        </header>

        <main class="container py-5 content-inner-max">
            <div class="mb-5 px-2">
                <h2 class="display-5 fw-black text-dark mb-2">Q&A 커뮤니티</h2>
                <p class="text-secondary fw-medium fs-5 opacity-75">캠핑 장비, 장소, 팁 등 궁금한 점을 고수들에게 물어보세요.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Filter & Action Bar -->
            <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between align-items-md-center gap-4 mb-5 px-2">
                <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4 fw-bold small">전체보기</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-light bg-white border border-secondary border-opacity-10 rounded-pill px-4 fw-bold small text-secondary btn-filter-hover transition-all">답변대기</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-light bg-white border border-secondary border-opacity-10 rounded-pill px-4 fw-bold small text-secondary btn-filter-hover transition-all">답변완료</button>
                </div>
                <button onclick="location.href='/qna/new'" class="btn btn-primary px-4 py-2.5 fw-bold shadow-lg border-0 d-flex align-items-center gap-2 rounded-3">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined fs-5">edit</span>
                    <span>질문하기</span>
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Question List -->
            <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3">
                <!-- Item 1: Pending -->
                <div class="fh-card question-item p-4 border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 transition-all bg-white">
                    <div class="d-flex gap-4">
                        <div class="status-icon-box status-pending shadow-sm"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">pending</span></div>
                        <div class="flex-grow-1">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                                <span class="badge bg-warning bg-opacity-10 text-warning fw-bold badge-res-status">답변대기</span>
                                <span class="text-secondary small fw-bold opacity-50">장비 추천</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="h6 fw-bold text-dark mb-3 hover-primary transition-colors cursor-pointer">겨울 캠핑용 등유 난로 브랜드 추천 부탁드립니다.</h3>
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 text-secondary text-xxs">
                                <span class="fw-black text-dark">캠핑초보22</span>
                                <span class="opacity-25">•</span>
                                <span>2023.11.24</span>
                                <span class="opacity-25">•</span>
                                <span class="d-flex align-items-center gap-1"><span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-14">visibility</span> 124</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex gap-2 align-self-start">
                            <button class="btn btn-sm fw-bold px-3 border-0 transition-all btn-edit-action">수정</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-sm fw-bold px-3 border-0 transition-all btn-delete-action">삭제</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Item 2: Completed -->
                <div class="fh-card question-item p-4 border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 transition-all bg-white">
                    <div class="d-flex gap-4">
                        <div class="status-icon-box status-completed shadow-sm"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">task_alt</span></div>
                        <div class="flex-grow-1">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                                <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary fw-bold badge-res-status">답변완료</span>
                                <span class="text-secondary small fw-bold opacity-50">캠핑장 정보</span>
                                <span class="lock-badge"><span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-14">lock</span> 수정제한</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="h6 fw-bold text-dark mb-3">경기도 인근에 별 잘 보이는 캠핑장 있을까요?</h3>
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 text-secondary text-xxs">
                                <span class="fw-black text-dark">별헤는밤</span>
                                <span class="opacity-25">•</span>
                                <span>2023.11.22</span>
                                <span class="opacity-25">•</span>
                                <span class="d-flex align-items-center gap-1"><span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-14">visibility</span> 342</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-end justify-content-between">
                            <span class="badge bg-primary text-white fw-bold px-2 py-1 badge-best-answer">BEST 답변 있음</span>
                            <div class="d-flex gap-2 mt-3">
                                <div class="custom-tooltip">
                                    <button class="btn btn-sm fw-bold px-3 border-0 opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed bg-light text-secondary rounded-3" disabled>수정</button>
                                    <span class="tooltip-text">답변이 완료되어 수정할 수 없습니다.</span>
                                </div>
                                <button class="btn btn-sm fw-bold px-3 border-0 transition-all btn-delete-action">삭제</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Pagination -->
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2 mt-5">
                <button class="btn btn-icon border border-secondary border-opacity-10 btn-light bg-white rounded-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined fs-6">chevron_left</span></button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary px-3 py-1.5 small fw-bold rounded-3">1</button>
                <button class="btn btn-light bg-white border border-secondary border-opacity-10 px-3 py-1.5 small fw-bold text-secondary rounded-3">2</button>
                <button class="btn btn-light bg-white border border-secondary border-opacity-10 px-3 py-1.5 small fw-bold text-secondary rounded-3">3</button>
                <button class="btn btn-icon border border-secondary border-opacity-10 btn-light bg-white rounded-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined fs-6">chevron_right</span></button>
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer class="fh-footer bg-white py-5 mt-5 border-top">
            <div class="container py-4 text-center text-md-start">
                <div class="row g-5">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="navbar-brand mb-4">
                            <div class="brand-icon small shadow-sm"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">forest</span></div>
                            <h2 class="brand-name h5">Forest Haven</h2>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-secondary small leading-relaxed max-w-sm">자연 속에서 진정한 휴식을 찾으세요. 포레스트 헤이븐은 당신의 완벽한 캠핑 경험을 위해 최고의 환경과 서비스를 제공합니다.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 text-md-end d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                        <p class="small text-secondary m-0 fw-bold">T. 1234-5678 | E. help@foresthaven.com</p>
                        <p class="small text-secondary m-0 opacity-50 mt-2">© 2024 Forest Haven. All rights reserved.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>

        <button class="btn-chatbot shadow-lg border-0 btn-chatbot-large rounded-circle bg-primary text-white">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined fs-1">chat_bubble</span>
        </button>
    </div>
{{> layout/footer}}
